sentences: Lakyn Heperi (born 28 April 1992) is an Australian-based New Zealand singer, songwriter and musician best known for appearing on The Voice Australia; he was eliminated at the quarterfinal stage.
His debut EP, Better Than That, was released on 16 November 2012 through Universal Music Australia.
On 16 November 2012, Lakyn released his first EP Better Than That through Universal Music Australia.
